The files "src/tests/reference_siphash_24.c" and 
"src/tests/reference_half_siphash_24.c" are copies of the reference C 
code provided by the original designers. This code does not get 
compiled into the library itself and is only used to verify 
correctness. The copyright information for these files follows:

